            "text_mGFdcK": {
              "type": "text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p>Plekify integrates your existing travel systems—like <a href=\"https://resrequest.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://resrequest.com/\">ResRequest</a> or <a href=\"https://wetu.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://wetu.com/\">Wetu</a>—with the power of <a href=\"https://shopify.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://shopify.com/\">Shopify</a>, the world's leading e-commerce platform.</p><p>Plekify automates the creation and updating of a custom Shopify travel site, enabling live availability and rates display on your site.</p><p>Customers checkout and pay using Shopify Checkout, the <a href=\"https://www.shopify.com/za/checkout\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.shopify.com/za/checkout\">best-converting checkout</a> on the internet.</p>",
