        "text_m6zWUy": {
          "type": "text",
          "name": "t:names.text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3>Own Your Bookings, Own Your Data</h3><p><strong>Maintain your own brand-identity</strong> throughout the reservations process.</p><p>Gain exclusive access to your own guest data, and harness the power of Shopify to impress these guests and<strong> accelerate your business</strong>.</p><h3>Effortless Multi-Language Reach</h3><p>Reach global travellers in up to 20 languages of your choice, for example <a href=\"https://plekify.com/\" title=\"https://plekify.com/\">English</a>, <a href=\"https://plekify.com/de\" title=\"https://plekify.com/de\">German</a>, <a href=\"https://plekify.com/fr\" title=\"https://plekify.com/fr\">French</a>, <a href=\"https://plekify.com/nl\" title=\"https://plekify.com/nl\">Dutch</a>, <a href=\"https://plekify.com/it\" title=\"https://plekify.com/it\">Italian</a>, <a href=\"https://plekify.com/es\" title=\"https://plekify.com/es\">Spanish</a>, <a href=\"https://plekify.com/pt\" title=\"https://plekify.com/pt\">Portuguese</a>, and <a href=\"https://plekify.com/zh-hans\" title=\"https://plekify.com/zh-hans\">Mandarin</a>, traditional <a href=\"https://plekify.com/zh-hant\" title=\"https://plekify.com/zh-hant\">Chinese</a>, <a href=\"https://plekify.com/af\" title=\"https://plekify.com/af\">Afrikaans</a>, <a href=\"https://plekify.com/xh\" title=\"https://plekify.com/xh\">Xhosa</a>, <a href=\"https://plekify.com/zu\" title=\"https://plekify.com/zu\">Zulu</a> and <a href=\"https://plekify.com/sw\" title=\"https://plekify.com/sw\">Swahili</a>.</p><p>Multi-language is excellent for conversion and also for Google SEO, as it multiplies your sites relevance and size...<strong>get discovered by more customers</strong>.</p><p>Every<strong> customers' first language</strong> is their preference, match it!</p><h3>Sell More with Add-Ons and Extras</h3><p>Offer curated experiences beyond rooms: spa treatments, game drives, transfers, wine tastings, and more. Guests add extras at checkout, increasing average order value by 20-30%.</p>",
