        "text_FnFJYi": {
          "type": "text",
          "name": "t:names.text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3>Powerful Marketing Built-In</h3><p>Re-activate and communicate in a personalised way with your previous customers using <a href=\"https://www.braze.com/partners/technology-partners/shopify\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.braze.com/partners/technology-partners/shopify\">Braze</a> or <a href=\"https://www.klaviyo.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Klaviyo</a>.</p><p>Recover abandoned carts, send post-stay reviews, and run loyalty programs.</p><p>Track campaigns across channels—your site, <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Instagram</a>, <a href=\"https://www.google.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Google</a>—from one dashboard.</p><h3>Financial Clarity and Scalability</h3><p>Connect to gateways like <a href=\"https://www.peachpayments.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Peach Payments</a> for direct-to-your-bank settlements.</p><p>Easily connect to modern ERP platforms such as <a href=\"https://apps.shopify.com/acumatica-cloud-erp\" target=\"_blank\">Acumatica Cloud ERP</a> or <a href=\"https://apps.shopify.com/oracle-netsuite\" target=\"_blank\">Oracle Netsuite</a>.</p><p>AirBnB's can easily connect accounting to <a href=\"https://quickbooks.intuit.com/\" target=\"_blank\">QuickBooks</a> or <a href=\"https://www.xero.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Xero</a>.</p><h3>Delight in Daily Use</h3><p>Intuitive usability for non-tech users, real-time analytics, and 24/7 support. Shopify is a delight—fast, reliable, and beautifully designed.</p>",
